{"tid":1633200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[][[特急]]] 保護何傳耀  爭取道德高地 新華社批何傳耀紀念中學為暴徒撐腰 讓法治難回學生內心","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T02:00:29.000Z","uid":324885,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f06e1adb61fee279b9f9069f6fdb7079cb3d9e92","tid":1633200,"uid":324885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:55:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484671-20191007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484671-20191007.htm&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4swxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=22027251\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484671-20191007.htm&h=70866aec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484671-20191007.htm</a> <br />\n新華社批何傳耀紀念中學為暴徒撐腰讓法治難回學生內心 <br />\n<br />\n建議各位保護學校<br />\n1. 各位校友和家長應該明早 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真面目</span></span>築人鏈<br />\n2. 召開緊急公開家教會和校友會大會，邀請辦學團體，校監和校長副校出席<br />\n3. 勇武暫時退場，即使藍絲、何妖等等在學校門外搞事，尤其<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要full gear出現</span>,，不要在學校門外出現衝突場面</span>，醜事、核突野盡量由黑警和藍絲自己食。<br />\n4.可以在何傳耀學校附近當眼位起連儂牆，文宣以保護學校、表揚學校不趕學生出校，列出對香港社會有貢獻、知名校友，以 保講學生為主，少粗口，多鬧黑警，多鬧福建邦。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 非何傳耀舊生，教育同路人"},{"pid":"ee6c280c46ef5a1e7681c05302c11e53fba47e68","tid":1633200,"uid":324885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"6e7812b8835de97eabe277a61e3d53873229eb37","tid":1633200,"uid":324885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:56:17.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"487c5edf9036c4da86da190d0633782515c57647","tid":1633200,"uid":324885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:56:30.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"3afb049b920014efb5aba06df9258a54f6f71945","tid":1633200,"uid":324885,"like":0,"disl