tyle=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>入錢入錢入錢！</strong></span><br />\n另外參考連登既食評，由於良心經營既關係，黃店食物質素一般都偏高，<br />\n絕對係win win雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n------------國際文宣------------<br />\n請將買返黎既貨物/食物/單據同排隊盛況<br />\n一齊用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"03e903aba4b14ca24c13eac903fc8df8f9884744","tid":1633200,"uid":300590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"972af924921009b5104797bf1d9a4096fb8ddd86","tid":1633200,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"點樣可以保護到佢地學校"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:07:28.000Z","msg":"首先要推起單野先<br />\n要單野變左焦點先保護到手足<br />\n怕人民日報聖旨單野重演<br />\nP牌推唔郁搵人幫手推!!"}]}